title: Arnette's Limited Edition Del the Funky Homosapien signature Fire Drill Launch
description:
Arnette has collaborated with Del the Funky Homosapien to bring two Limited Edition signature colorways of the Fire Drill available at Sunglass Hut starting October 20th.

The Del edition of the Fire Drill features a matte black frame that dissolves out into purples on the lower rims and temples. Del's signature logo is featured on one temple tip and the iconic Hieroglyphics logo gets placement on the other. It's available with either blue mirror or polarized gray faded lenses.

To celebrate the release of the new Del Fire Drill sunglasses, Arnette and Sunglass Hut will be hosting an in-store meet-and-greet with Del at the Sunglass Hut store in Union Square, San Francisco (170 Geary Street, San Francisco) October 27th 6pm-7:30pm and will be throwing a special product release party at Public Works (161 Erie St., San Francisco) at 9pm. Del, along with The Souls of Mischief, Casual and Bukue one will be performing LIVE!
